    "translation": "",
    "context": "_event.m.Injured.getName() + \" suffers \" + injury.getNameOnly()"
  },
  {
    "key": "285db421dde6f5bb8b0df2eb451a601f6425d4083ee4ded41980c845a8d30c76",
    "original": "Along the road...",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Title = \"Along the road...\""
  },
  {
    "key": "52ea67359dfa70ce35169fd2493590d8371919161a7fb2e28e322863448b9a87",
    "original": "Farewell.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Farewell.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "debdf5388dadaa08f44d2bd31da4379538a6347f0b13b10e18f8d31466be6e04",
    "original": "I hope it was worth it.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"I hope it was worth it.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b9865f5bfd540758d0f798bee9f045fee68153fc5e505fb67e34c523e35c4d8b",
    "original": "Let us help you get your cart on the road again.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Let us help you get your cart on the road again.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "de1703ef6aef0b2cad630bed18a112927af7c55767bbed73aecf0220435c9f9b",
    "original": "Men, take everything we can use from the cart!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Men, take everything we can use from the cart!\""
  },
  {
    "key": "271b88e120f9c741f38f0bb4a0144a5f8cf174fb18525c3e083359b8af2d511f",
    "original": "Store everything, we're moving on.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Store everything, we're moving on.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "a4ef24823fd4bccbc279fe92737c63ae8d2399b3bfd69506e742459d33d9bae4",
    "original": "We have no time for this.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"We have no time for this.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "85d13cf4d5f8d972cb9d6de67c9cc3128758d8462dd3293693b2bcc94257ec0e",
    "original": "You gain ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You gain \" + food.getName()"
  },
  {
    "key": "75c45e6b8866c7aacf8d3a14cae5d644d278d2f53ab2cc835118e64cc9d12404",
    "original": "You gain [color=",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You gain [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveEventValue + \"]+\" + amount + \"[/color] Medical Supplies.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "75c45e6b8866c7aacf8d3a14cae5d644d278d2f53ab2cc835118e64cc9d12404",
    "original": "You gain [color=",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You gain [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveEventValue + \"]+\" + amount + \"[/color] Tools and Supplies.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "90d1d1e14419b406685545b01911e77412785eb04fc068851ba296e038243087",
    "original": "[/color] Medical Supplies.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You gain [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveEventValue + \"]+\" + amount + \"[/color] Medical Supplies.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "4f6fdae815a1a55f343cb81c44a49a2f58d24813d9ddd4b53248ae1d052807b8",
    "original": "[/color] Tools and Supplies.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You gain [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveEventValue + \"]+\" + amount + \"[/color] Tools and Supplies.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "fd4148198ae77a6aa6e6751635917505ce92c93f4cd18ee9687475284a133aaf",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]The merchant is scared in your presence, but you quickly disarm him of his fears. A few brothers are ordered to get the cart back onto the path. They do it as fast as hardy men can, but when it's over one of them cries out and doubles over.\n\nThe trader, eyes wide with renewed horror, quickly offers you some provisions as a token of his gratitude. Maybe he thinks you'll punish him for the injuries? Regardless, the supplies will be a welcome addition for the days to come.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]The merchant is scared in your presence, but you quickly disarm him of his fears. A few brothers are ordered to get the cart back onto the path. They do it as fast as hardy men can, but when it's over one of them cries out and doubles over.\\n\\nThe trader, eyes wide with renewed horror, quickly offers you some provisions as a token of his gratitude. Maybe he thinks you'll punish him for the injuries? Regardless, the supplies will be a welcome addition for the days to come.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7b0b311242fe06ad19c0e72b4dc9320b60d0ecbe47de06401e08d1cf74c764bf",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]While marching down the road, you find a man with a broken cart by the side of the path. By the wagon there is a donkey standing idle and as defeated as a donkey can look. The trader looks a little better than that and your appearance seems to have scared him. He rears up, backing away momentarily.%SPEECH_ON%Have you come to take my things? If so, you needn't kill me. Take what you want.%SPEECH_OFF%",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]While marching down the road, you find a man with a broken cart by the side of the path. By the wagon there is a donkey standing idle and as defeated as a donkey can look. The trader looks a little better than that and your appearance seems to have scared him. He rears up, backing away momentarily.%SPEECH_ON%Have you come to take my things? If so, you needn't kill me. Take what you want.%SPEECH_OFF%\""
  },
  {
    "key": "178f32c09610eb67c9e7b6f9de4da144368b43822ae8630e28e5d53cb5e014c7",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]You disarm the man from his fears and order a few of the %companyname%'s finest to get the wagon back on the road. They make short work of it, the trader looking rather impressed by their efficiency. With his wares back on the road, he offers a few tokens of gratitude right off the wagon itself. These provisions will be useful in the days to come.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]You disarm the man from his fears and order a few of the %companyname%'s finest to get the wagon back on the road. They make short work of it, the trader looking rather impressed by their efficiency. With his wares back on the road, he offers a few tokens of gratitude right off the wagon itself. These provisions will be useful in the days to come.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "cba61d72d7395787566bc81f25654f363874b50124c56c26f0ec564046c9d5ca",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]You order the men to search the cart and take what they can. %randombrother% draws his sword and looks ready to slay the donkey, the animal looking stupidly at its own mortality in the reflection of the blade. The merchant cries out and you hold your hand out, staying the execution.%SPEECH_ON%Leave the draught animal where it stands.%SPEECH_OFF%The trader offers meager thanks as a line of your men walk behind him, his very goods in their hands.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]You order the men to search the cart and take what they can. %randombrother% draws his sword and looks ready to slay the donkey, the animal looking stupidly at its own mortality in the reflection of the blade. The merchant cries out and you hold your hand out, staying the execution.%SPEECH_ON%Leave the draught animal where it stands.%SPEECH_OFF%The trader offers meager thanks as a line of your men walk behind him, his very goods in their hands.\""
  }
]